quote.summary: Tianjin Jinran Public Utilities Co Ltd is principally engaged in the operation and management of gas pipeline infrastructure and the sales of piped gas. The Company operates through four business segments. The Sales of Pipeline Natural Gas segment is engaged in the sales of piped gas to industrial and residential users. The Gas Pipeline Connection segment is engaged in the provision of piped gas connection services. The Gas Pipeline Transportation segment is engaged in the transportation of gas. Sales of Gas Appliances and Other Commodity segment is engaged in sales of gas appliances and gas related products. The Company is also engaged in gas pipeline infrastructure operations and management, leasing of owned premises, and leasing of gas filling station facilities operated through its subsidiaries. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in China.
